* Ingestion Tool\nDecision Framework
** Enterprise App / DB Source?
***_ Yes → Lakeflow Connect Managed
** Files in Cloud Storage?
***_ Ongoing → Auto Loader
***_ One-time → COPY INTO
** Real-time / Kafka?
***_ Lakeflow Connect Standard
***_ or Structured Streaming
** Unsupported DB / Custom Logic?
***_ JDBC/ODBC Notebook
** Azure Ecosystem Orchestration?
***_ Azure Data Factory
@endmindmap
